<div class="bg-warm-100 py-12 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h3 class="tr font-serif font-light text-2xl tracking-tight text-ink">Stay Updated</h3>
    <p class="tr mt-3 text-sm text-ink-soft">Get tips on decluttering, moving, and keeping your space clear.</p>
